# Conventional Commit Format
# <type>: <concise description>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, refactor, test, chore, perf, style, ci
#
# Examples:
#   feat: add DNS-over-HTTPS fallback
#   fix: resolve EPG channel icon parsing for self-closing tags
#   docs: update AGENTS.md with new task-to-file mapping
#   refactor: extract cache logic to separate module
#   test: add integration tests for streaming endpoints
#
# Keep subject under 72 chars. Use body for details.
#
# If this commit is for a kanban task, reference it:
#   docs(task_1748397912_abc12345): ...
